## complex

A complex number from a real *r* and an imaginary *i* number.

	( r:Float i:Float -- Float )

Example:

| Input     | Stack
|-----------|---------------
| `6      ` | `6` 
| `12     ` | `6 \| 12` 
| `complex` | `6+12i`
